### Excel Reports API Testing

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Get Employee Directory Report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/employee-directory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Department Report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Attendance Report (All employees, last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Attendance Report with date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/attendance?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Attendance Report for specific employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/attendance?employeeId=1&startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Salary Report (All departments, last 12 months)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/salary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Salary Report with date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/salary?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Salary Report for specific department
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/salary?departmentId=1&startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Department Managers Report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/department-managers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Comprehensive Report (Multiple sheets)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/comprehensive
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Attendance Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/attendance/summary?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}